{"tid":1842103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"TUNS仲要返工 到底應唔應該","createTime":"2020-01-25T13:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T16:11:48.000Z","uid":56772,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"22cf28d0645f0dbd37fc458d52029cd0a087a286","tid":1842103,"uid":56772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"未grad又兩頭唔到岸<br />\n未係正式staff<br />\n保險cover又唔夠<br />\nPre-RN Tuns要返都仲接受同明白<br />\n但一班year 3-5要返我覺得真係推佢地出黎死<br />\n始終clinical experience唔係咁多<br />\n佢地份糧唔包㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果staff咗我願意返<br />\n但未staff又保障唔到自己<br />\n我覺得好唔公平囉！<br />\n見到身邊同學俾人當condom一齊抽生死籤覺得好嬲好唔開心啊！<br />\n<br />\n根本有FTOCC班人都可以亂講<br />\nDllm香港政府、HA同中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e602ad58d4bb4750b4e01c209893990b2345979","tid":1842103,"uid":229886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"tuns當parttime<br />\n應該可以射波？<br />\n利申唔識"},{"pid":"a1b440fb230f61bea62b63c1ad21bde2c2b81593","tid":1842103,"uid":281401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"NO, you are not essential to the ward."},{"pid":"c0f2a9061879c43fb9ce07623b71550e1c99581b","tid":1842103,"uid":56772,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6e602ad58d4bb4750b4e01c209893990b2345979","tid":1842103,"uid":229886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"tuns當parttime<br />\n應該可以射波？<br />\n利申唔識"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"有見到有人俾人一齊拎去抽生死簽 雖然唔知最後點處理 但一開波已經好ridiculous <br />\n仲有某D WM勁harsh話tuns唔係student nurse係簽咗contract<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8cf263e53ffb7304dec311746ccf4fb6d313e20","tid":1842103,"uid":53683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"條命你自己<br />\nstaff都諗緊做唔做既同時<br />\n你tuns同佢搏命?<br />\n兩大醫科都唔出clinical啦"},{